          <p>Labor. Everyone in the hotel business knows this is the number one most draining cost on the industry. Small motels and large five-star operations alike deal with the impossibility of automation every day: in most cases, it’s simply not practical to replace the hours an employee spends checking every single room once or twice over. <a href="/iiot-at-work/stories/minibar-systems">Read more.</a></p>
